    "status": {
      "$description": "The four status hue families, each exposing the steps both themes consume. Light uses 100 (soft tint) + 700 (solid); dark flips to 900 (dark tint) + 300 (light solid). A brand may shift these hues, but red=error / green=success conventions are near-universal \u2014 change with care.",
